      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to own. It's in really solid shape, super clean inside and out, and drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with you right away. Perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, well-loved car that still has so much life left in it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
