    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a double-VANOS variable valve timing system. Mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the mechanical engagement is absolute. The chassis remains composed, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and refreshed suspension bushings. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive valve clearance adjustment and a cooling system overhaul to ensure optimal thermal management. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with spirited use, the high-revving straight-six pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. Equipped with the variable M Differential Lock for superior corner-exit traction, this is a mechanically sound, driver-focused machine optimized for the B-roads.",
      "price": 32500.0,
