    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of pride of ownership, presenting in excellent shape for its age. The exterior finish retains a high luster, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use, while the alloy wheels remain crisp and clean. Inside, the cabin is a pristine, smoke-free environment; the upholstery is free of tears or significant wear, and every power feature\u2014from the responsive touchscreen to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a strict regimen of synthetic oil changes and recent preventative maintenance, ensuring the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision. With a quiet ride and a solid service history, this is a dependable and attractive choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle that needs nothing but a new driver.",
      "price": 33800.0,
