    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking for a new home for this awesome ride! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in really nice shape, making it the perfect choice if you want a solid, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It drives like a dream and is ready for all your upcoming road trips and weekend adventures. I\u2019ve truly enjoyed owning this car, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Drop me a message if you want to come take it for a spin!",
