    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is paired with a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, offering a tactile connection to the variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, ensuring the chassis remains composed under high lateral loads. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with a well-loved machine, the mechanical synchronization and throttle linearity remain exceptional.",
